Rating: 4
I substituted spiced rum for the dark, and cooked the crepes in a skillet rather than in the oven. It worked just as well, but I ended up with a lot (!) of crepes - tons more than 16. I put the rest in the freezer between wax paper, so tbd how they store. Great recipe, and super easy, even for a crepe novice like myself.

