I used a little butter, sugar and lemon instead of jam and it was dreamy. Don't tell anyone, but I used tonic water instead of soda...shhhh.

Rating: 3
Not very difficult to make. My wife and I really enjoyed it. Fortunately, I made extra crepes and will have it with another jam in a couple of days.